WEBVTT

NOTE
Faithful transcript of the Evolus ICON event recap, mirroring the
film's own burned-in captions (operator-verified — docs/DECISIONS.md
2026-07-21). Speech is manufacturer/event content carried under the
recorded override.

00:00.000 --> 00:04.500
[Music]

00:04.500 --> 00:08.500
(Dr. Benji Dhillon) Hi, I'm Doctor Benji Dhillon,
and I'm here in Newport Beach

00:08.500 --> 00:12.500
at the Evolus headquarters
for the first ever Icon Experience.

00:12.500 --> 00:16.000
And I'm really excited to share a room
with like minded people.

00:16.000 --> 00:34.000
[Music]

00:34.000 --> 00:36.500
(David Moatazedi, Evolus CEO)
Our purpose is very simple.

00:36.500 --> 00:40.500
We want that beauty experience
to be an incredible one for the consumer.

00:40.500 --> 00:44.500
(Event attendee) to be able to speak with other
providers and just gain some experience.

00:44.500 --> 00:48.500
to keep up and education is really
to keep up with modern technology.

00:48.500 --> 00:51.000
(Kristen Dee, RN) I am obsessed
with continuing education.

00:51.000 --> 00:53.500
It's so important

00:55.500 --> 00:59.500
and Evolus has done a next level
representation of what that means.

01:00.500 --> 01:03.000
(Ana Trevathan, APRN) The best part is
learning from some of the world leaders.

01:03.000 --> 01:05.000
(Rui Avelar, MD) Compared to Botox

01:05.000 --> 01:08.500
we saw a statistical difference
of superiority

01:08.500 --> 01:10.500
against that Day 3 with the onset.

01:10.500 --> 01:14.500
(Kourtney Cavallio, Evolus) We hope our customers
leave here from this event with some really great

01:14.500 --> 01:18.500
tips and tricks that they can use in their own
practices when they get back, and also leave with

01:18.500 --> 01:22.000
some really friendships and relationships
from injectors across the country.

01:22.000 --> 01:26.800
[Dramatic music]
